{"tid":1550640,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對面如果有幾個恐怖分子衝緊埋黎點算？","createTime":"2019-09-07T16:56:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T17:18:52.000Z","uid":19092,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"712a691c04a020d13737644e2bf483260d9564d3","tid":1550640,"uid":19092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:56:33.000Z","msg":"萬一你地比恐怖分子追殺緊。<br />\n假設對方5-10人， 手足20-30人， 而你地想救人，係應該見邊個恐怖分子企係到就撲邊個。 咩都唔洗諗， 攬住佢攬住佢佢就襲擊唔到你。 如果手足人數多， 3個攬埋去中意點打就點打<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d3dfa098d2a3b33c9053e8894e82b0d7af2638b","tid":1550640,"uid":19092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:57:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ff579d0d51e1417ec173ffb7945e9411fdcea6d","tid":1550640,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:57:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5b1bc53ebc92acb8157d64825fd9d7dad3b3c786","tid":1550640,"uid":19092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:58:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9471a4b1b7789958e84442e3f0e581ef8ac095d0","tid":1550640,"uid":19092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:00:30.000Z","msg":"唔好再犯同一樣既錯， 你睇班恐怖分子點足人， 一定係埋身撲低你再幾個一齊㩒住你黎打。<br />\n<br />\n你地要記住你幾好武功都冇用， 埋身人多就象都死。"},{"pid":"7cdb697a7a71fc1ae2d4d5de5a5bb56a9e17d1f3","tid":1550640,"uid":19092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:00:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"649689eb8dccef689c69ec6b6da416aa4086a3a1","tid":1550640,"uid":183758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:01:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a581d724b42a3c8749cdf2f14438c27b2aaa51fd","tid":1550640,"uid":19092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:01:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5427fa488591219afc849a2fa1069a0f9a57e99","tid":1550640,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:01:36.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我警告你班仆街！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">聽日啲<span style=\"color: red;\">美國</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">國旗</span>唔好周圍掉！<br />\n路邊見到唔該即刻幫手執返！<br />\n完咗活動攞返屋企收藏！</span></span><br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/evxvjtB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FevxvjtB.jpg&h=73325a8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"> 快啲聽熟加背歌詞，<br />\n唱得莊嚴啲！</span>\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPWMy7Rpk5Bo&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQCx1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=5dc77540\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo</a><br />\n</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n分段背易啲背：<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Oh, say can you see,</span></span><br />\nBy the dawn's early light,<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">What so proudly we hailed,</span><br />\nAt the twilight's last gleaming?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Whose broad stripes and bright stars,</span><br />\nThrough the perilous fight,<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">O'er the ramparts we watched,</span><br />\nWere so gallantly streaming.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">And the rocket's red glare,</span><br />\nThe bombs bursting in air,<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Gave proof through the night,</span><br />\nThat our flag was still there.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Oh say does that star spangled banner yet wave,</span><br />\n<br />\nFor the land of the free, and the home of the brave.</div><br />\n<br />\n聽日見！</span>"},{"pid":"0c290c6b5150257f3b7dad15c7d7827e223a56c2","tid":1550640,"uid":19092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:02:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28e2edb2ee15259052988ca50e8376d238b4a3ac","tid":1550640,"uid":8600,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:02:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23283ed7733240a2f233ea3c8e9d00fbc987b620","tid":1550640,"uid":19092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28e2edb2ee15259052988ca50e8376d238b4a3ac","tid":1550640,"uid":8600,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:02:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:03:36.000Z","msg":"係唔好比對方企到係到， 一落地佢就死撚緊"},{"pid":"f94413127f716f34fd5c356b66fac009c53ea421","tid":1550640,"uid":19092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c